1. **Feature catalogs** — 24 `feature-catalog/` trees exist across `.opencode/skills/`; 0 mention the compiled router.
2. **Benchmark logic** — the Lane C skill-benchmark (`.opencode/skills/system-deep-loop/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/`) observes the LEGACY replay only; never invokes the compiled path. The 3 scorer files (`router-replay.cjs`, `score-skill-benchmark.cjs`, `load-playbook-scenarios.cjs`) are FROZEN — never edited.
3. **Manual-testing playbooks** — 39 `manual-testing-playbook/` trees exist; 0 have new-router scenarios.
4. **Durable results** — the only compiled-vs-legacy proof (route-gold) lives inside `.opencode/specs/`; 0 archived in the durable `.opencode/skills/<hub>/benchmark/<run-label>/` locations.

