   274	- [ ] Every root catalog entry links to exactly one per-feature file
   275	- [ ] Every per-feature file includes frontmatter with `title` and `description`
   276	
   277	Content:
   278	- [ ] Every root catalog entry has Description, Current Reality, and Source Files callout
   279	- [ ] Every per-feature file has `OVERVIEW`, `HOW IT WORKS`, `SOURCE FILES`, and `SOURCE METADATA`
   280	- [ ] Source-file tables are specific and meaningful
