   199	Root summaries should be concise but useful:
   200	
   201	- Provide enough context to understand what each scenario covers.
   202	- Preview operator intent and prompt shape.
   203	- Do not duplicate the full execution matrix from the per-feature file.
   204	
   205	Root-to-feature rule: the root document explains package-level policy; per-feature files carry scenario-specific execution truth.
   206	
   207	### Per-Feature File Responsibilities
   208	
   209	Each per-feature file is the canonical scenario contract for one feature ID.
   210	
   211	Required per-feature section order:
   212	
   213	1. `## 1. OVERVIEW`
   214	2. `## 2. SCENARIO CONTRACT`
   215	3. `## 3. TEST EXECUTION`
   216	4. `## 4. REFERENCES` or `## 4. SOURCE FILES`
   217	5. `## 5. SOURCE METADATA`
   218	
