.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/015-routing-coverage-activation-verification/001-research/research/findings-registry.json:204:      "finding": "Prior LUNA route runs repeatedly exhausted the 150-second ceiling, so model timeout must be separated from routing correctness.",
